## 0. Design Philosophy (Foundation)

**Design goals**

* Calm, confident, familiar
* Native-feeling on iOS
* Clear hierarchy, no clutter
* Works with Dynamic Type & Dark Mode

**Core principles**

* Clarity > decoration
* One primary action per screen
* Progressive disclosure everywhere
* System components first, custom only when needed

---

# 1. Global Design System

## 1.1 Typography (Exact)

ðŸ‘‰ **Use Apple System Font (SF Pro)**
*(React Native: default system font, do NOT specify custom fonts)*

| Purpose             | iOS Text Style | Size | Weight   |
| ------------------- | -------------- | ---- | -------- |
| Large Screen Titles | LargeTitle     | ~34  | Bold     |
| Section Titles      | Title2         | ~22  | Semibold |
| Card Titles         | Headline       | ~17  | Semibold |
| Body Text           | Body           | ~16  | Regular  |
| Secondary Text      | Subheadline    | ~15  | Regular  |
| Captions            | Caption1       | ~12  | Regular  |
| Button Text         | Headline       | ~17  | Semibold |

âœ… **Dynamic Type enabled everywhere**

---

## 1.2 Color System (Semantic & Apple-style)

### Primary Brand Color

**Ceylon Green**

```
#1F7A5C
```

Used for:

* Primary buttons
* Selected states
* Highlights
* Date selection

---

### Semantic Colors (Use system equivalents)

| Purpose              | Light   | Dark    |
| -------------------- | ------- | ------- |
| Background           | #FFFFFF | #000000 |
| Secondary Background | #F2F2F7 | #1C1C1E |
| Card Background      | #FFFFFF | #2C2C2E |
| Primary Text         | #000000 | #FFFFFF |
| Secondary Text       | #6E6E73 | #A1A1A6 |
| Disabled             | #C7C7CC | #3A3A3C |
| Divider              | #E5E5EA | #38383A |

ðŸ‘‰ In RN use:

* `bg-white dark:bg-black`
* `text-black dark:text-white`
* etc.

---

## 1.3 Spacing System (Consistent Rhythm)

| Size | Value |
| ---- | ----- |
| XS   | 4     |
| S    | 8     |
| M    | 16    |
| L    | 24    |
| XL   | 32    |

ðŸ‘‰ Most screens use **16px horizontal padding**

---

## 1.4 Corner Radius

| Component     | Radius |
| ------------- | ------ |
| Buttons       | 12     |
| Cards         | 16     |
| Images        | 16     |
| Bottom Sheets | 24     |

---

## 1.5 Shadows (Subtle Only)

Apple-style shadows are **soft and minimal**.

```
shadowColor: #000
shadowOpacity: 0.08
shadowRadius: 8
shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 4 }
```

