## Apple-Level UX Details (This Scores Marks)

### Validation

* Inline validation
* No error popups
* Clear helper text

### Autosave

* Save progress automatically
* Resume later

### Accessibility

* Dynamic Type
* Large tap targets
* VoiceOver-friendly labels
